Rating: 4
I made this dessert when it first appeared for a friend and her family who LOVES chocolate. This is not an easy dessert to make (as one reviewer stated) and requires quite a bit of time. I used a 10" springform pan and lined it with two layers of parchemnt, then sprayed it with a non-stick spray. This greatly helped removal from the pan. I removed the cake from the pan after it had cooled (placed it on the serving platter)and then refrigerated it overnight. This cake WOWED my friend and her family. It is VERY rich and a small slice went a long way.

