Rating: 4
This is a great recipe. Have made it serveral times now always with a great response! A suggestion for easier servering. Try using parchment paper on the bottom of the pan. Simply spray pan like recipe says then add parchment paper that is a little bigger in diameter than pan bottom. Once paper is in place spray it too. Then proceed as recipe says. Should be a little easier to remove from pan bottom and move to a serving tray.

